# Step 1: Capture the workload using SQL Server Profiler.\n# Save the captured file in RML Format (.trc).\n\n# Step 2: Convert .trc file to Preprocessed Log Directory (using Distributed Replay Preprocess Controller).\nDReplay preprocess -m <ControllerMachineName> -i "C:\Path\To\TraceFile.trc" -d "C:\PreProcessedLogDirectory"\n\n# Step 3: Configure replay settings in a configuration file (replayclient.xml).\n\n# Step 4: Use Distributed Replay Client to replay the workload.\nDReplay client -m <ControllerMachineName> -f "C:\PreProcessedLogDirectory"